I hear things daily like: üëá ‚ÄúHow can I get more people to my landing page?‚Äù ‚ÄúHow can I get traffic for cheaper?‚Äù ‚ÄúHow can we increase conversions?‚Äù Oh... This is my favorite... ü§£ü§£ ‚ÄúHow come my funnel isn‚Äôt converting?‚Äù What most people don‚Äôt realize is that you can send all the traffic you want to your offer... BUT if your offer isn‚Äôt of value, you‚Äôll never convert anything... Here‚Äôs my 10-point offer checklist I look at when crafting my offers... üëá

1. Will my ideal audience resonate with this offer?

2. What‚Äôs a really big pain point they have? 
3. How can my offer be the solution to that pain? 
4. Will my solution actually solve the problem? 
5. Am I selling something that‚Äôs ethical?

6. Will people want to share it with their friends because of their outcome? 
7. Is the value worth 10X the price? 
8. Will the solution return their investment? If so, how long? 
9. Will they want to buy other offers higher up in my value ladder after buying my initial offer? 
10. Will this be a long-term customer after making this purchase? 
You see, most people just craft an offer without any strategy, which is why most of your funnels/campaigns are failing... Only after I go through my 10-point offer checklist and make sure it all makes sense... Only then I make an offer... ü§ó
